Detailed Description

This folder contains drivers for hardware on the Olimex AVR-USB-162 boards (http://www.olimex.com/dev/avr-usb-162.html). The header files in this folder should not be included directly in user applications; the similarly named dispatch header files located in the parent Board directory should be included instead.
